{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01U2XHgCmEjDabHjWeus6JjE","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### Ran Playwright code\n```js\nawait page.goto('http://localhost:3000/modules/module-1/ai-vs-hype');\n```\n### Page\n- Page URL: http://localhost:3000/modules/module-1/ai-vs-hype\n- Page Title: AI vs. the Hype Machine — Epiphany Learn\n### Snapshot\n```yaml\n- generic [active] [ref=e1]:\n  - main [ref=e2]:\n    - generic [ref=e4]:\n      - generic [ref=e5]:\n        - link \"Modules\" [ref=e6] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: /modules\n        - generic [ref=e7]: /\n        - link \"What AI Actually Is\" [ref=e8] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: /modules/module-1\n        - generic [ref=e9]: /\n        - generic [ref=e10]: AI vs. the Hype Machine\n      - generic [ref=e11]: 1 of 4\n    - generic [ref=e14]:\n      - generic [ref=e15]:\n        - generic [ref=e16]:\n          - generic [ref=e17]: 7 min read\n          - generic [ref=e18]: ·\n          - generic [ref=e19]: +50 XP\n        - heading \"AI vs. the Hype Machine\" [level=1] [ref=e20]\n        - paragraph [ref=e21]: What it actually does — and doesn't do\n      - article [ref=e22]:\n        - heading \"AI vs. the Hype Machine\" [level=1] [ref=e23]\n        - paragraph [ref=e24]:\n          - text: \"Every week there's a new headline:\"\n          - emphasis [ref=e25]: \"\\\"AI will replace all jobs.\\\"\"\n          - emphasis [ref=e26]: \"\\\"AI can think like a human.\\\"\"\n          - emphasis [ref=e27]: \"\\\"AI is sentient.\\\"\"\n        - paragraph [ref=e28]: Most of it is noise. Let's cut through it.\n        - separator [ref=e29]\n        - heading \"What AI Actually Does\" [level=2] [ref=e30]\n        - paragraph [ref=e31]:\n          - text: At its core, AI is\n          - strong [ref=e32]: pattern recognition at massive scale\n          - text: .\n        - paragraph [ref=e33]: You feed a system enormous amounts of data. It finds patterns. It uses those patterns to make predictions or generate outputs.\n        - paragraph [ref=e34]: That's it.\n        - list [ref=e35]:\n          - listitem [ref=e36]: Show it millions of dog photos → it learns to recognize dogs\n          - listitem [ref=e37]: Show it billions of sentences → it learns to predict what word comes next\n          - listitem [ref=e38]: Show it thousands of X-rays → it learns to spot abnormalities\n        - paragraph [ref=e39]:\n          - strong [ref=e40]: There is no \"thinking\" happening.\n          - text: There's no understanding, no feelings, no consciousness. AI is extraordinarily good at finding patterns humans would miss — but it has no idea what those patterns\n          - emphasis [ref=e41]: mean\n          - text: .\n        - separator [ref=e42]\n        - heading \"The Marketing vs. The Reality\" [level=2] [ref=e43]\n        - button \"? AI is intelligent ▼\" [ref=e44] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - generic [ref=e45]:\n            - generic [ref=e46]:\n              - generic [ref=e47]: \"?\"\n              - generic [ref=e48]: AI is intelligent\n            - generic [ref=e49]: ▼\n        - button \"? AI understands you ▼\" [ref=e50] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - generic [ref=e51]:\n            - generic [ref=e52]:\n              - generic [ref=e53]: \"?\"\n              - generic [ref=e54]: AI understands you\n            - generic [ref=e55]: ▼\n        - button \"? AI will take over ▼\" [ref=e56] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - generic [ref=e57]:\n            - generic [ref=e58]:\n              - generic [ref=e59]: \"?\"\n              - generic [ref=e60]: AI will take over\n            - generic [ref=e61]: ▼\n        - paragraph [ref=e62]: Click each card to see the reality behind the hype.\n        - separator [ref=e63]\n        - heading \"Why This Matters for You\" [level=2] [ref=e64]\n        - paragraph [ref=e65]: \"If you understand what AI actually is — a pattern-matching engine — you can:\"\n        - li